text: Bul-Kaypanovo () is a rural locality (a selo) and the administrative center of Bul-Kaypanovsky Selsoviet, Tatyshlinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 682 as of 2010. There are 11 streets. == Geography == It is located 7 km from Verkhniye Tatyshly. == References == Category:Rural localities in Tatyshlinsky District
title: Bul-Kaypanovo
